@node How2Play

                            MazezaM

MazezaM (pronounced "may-zam") is a simple puzzle game. You enter the
mazezam on the left and you have to get to the exit on the right by
pushing rows of blocks left and right. If you get stuck you can
retry the mazezam, but this will cost you a life.

Use the arrow keys or the joystick to move.

Press R to give up the current try.
Press Q to give up current game.
Press M to switch the music on/off.

From the menus:

New Game     - to start new game.

About        - to see some copyright text.

Quit         - for exit.

On the title screen press Return to advance the speech.

